I thought this was great - have made it twice and both times it was well received. The flavor is good, it's easy and the sauce can be made ahead and used at the last minute. I didn't give it 4 forks because I just have trouble giving a vegetable 4 forks - holdover from childhood maybe. Would absolutely make again.

