Just OK. Not sure why the recipe calls for boiling the broccolini -- I usually steam them, and wish I had after tasting these, as they were mushy and soft (even after reducing cooking time by a minute or two). Definitely use smaller garlic cloves, as the taste of raw garlic is a little overpowering.

